Saudi Arabia’s Business Optimism Index in Third Quarter Falls

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-07-12T11:47:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/saudi-arabia-s-business-optimism-index-in-third-quarter-falls.html
Saudi Arabia ’s Business Optimism
Index for the non-hydrocarbon industries fell to 52 points in
the third quarter from 68 in the previous quarter,  National
Commercial Bank  and Dun & Bradstreet said in a statement today.  The third-quarter reading signals that Saudi business
sentiment is falling amid weakening global recovery, according
to the e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
